name: Wheel of fortune
description:
I took this picture when I was in Osaka, Japan.
That day was in a middle of November, it was a chill day.
The sky was clearly blue. 

I was walking with someone.
That was the first and last time I walked with 'him'.
Life is going on as the Ferris wheel.
I don't know when will I meet 'him' again.

It depends on the wheel of fortune.
